  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The present study is a randomized pilot study, overweight/obese adolescent and young PCOS
      subjects will be assigned into two groups: Taichi arm and control arm. Hormonal profile and
      metabolic profile will be determined.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
