    <intervention_name>Taichi</intervention_name>
    <description>The program of Taichi training consisted of 60 minutes exercise sessions, 3 days per week for 12 weeks, based on their original level of physical activity. Each session comprised 40 minutes of Taichi training plus a 10-minute warm-up and cool-down. The Taichi training was instructed by the same experienced Taichi instructors who were qualified in the teaching of Taichi. The 24 forms of simplified Taichi recommended as the popular health sport by the General Administration of Sport of China were applied.</description>
